name: AGENT DOGE by Virtuals
description: AGENT DOGE ($AIDOGE) is launched on Virtuals Protocol. Token is a combination of a meme token and a defi token. It's purpose is to assist in the modern manhattan project of our times, the Department Of Government Efficiency. The agent constantly review government contracts and reports. Then the agent posts it's the findings on the Agent Doge X account. https://x.com/agentdoge007 The utility + defi aspect of the token comes with the agents plan to work with other agents. The founders of the token will create a fund to partner with profitable trading agents, and then use those profits to buy back and burn tokens. So, other token holders can experience an appreciating asset based on the partner trading agents.
